                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-277" type="given" value="STEPHEN"></interp>STEPHEN TAYLOR</persName>
                  </hi>. He had it in his hand, he was not a yard from me—I caught his right arm, and he threw it down with his left hand—he ran away from me.</p>
